### Miltenyi Biotec

#### TCR α/β RNA Profiling Kit, human

==`miltenyi-human-rna-tcr-profiling`==
·
[:octicons-link-16: Link](https://www.miltenyibiotec.com/US-en/products/tcr-a-b-rna-profiling-kit-human.html#130-139-385)
·
[:octicons-mark-github-16: Code](https://github.com/milaboratory/mixcr/blob/develop/src/main/resources/presets/protocols/miltenyi.yaml)
·
[:octicons-mortar-board-16: Tutorial](../guides/miltenyi-human-rna-tcr-profiling.md)

Allows to obtain human TCR alpha and beta CDR3 repertoires for different types of available RNA material, with high sensitivity and UMI-based accuracy. 

![](pics/miltenyi-multiplex-tcr-light.svg#only-light)
![](pics/miltenyi-multiplex-tcr-dark.svg#only-dark)

Example:
```shell
mixcr analyze miltenyi-human-rna-tcr-profiling \
      input_R1.fastq.gz \
      input_R2.fastq.gz \
      result 
```